● code/main.py is done — it was actually an empty 0-byte placeholder already in
  the repo scaffold (along with an empty code/evaluation/ dir), so I overwrote
  it rather than creating fresh.

  What it does:
  - Parses --input, --output, --dataset-dir (sensible defaults:
  dataset/claims.csv, repo-root output.csv, dataset/).
  - Loads .env via python-dotenv.
  - Reads claims.csv with pandas (dtype=str, so things like user_id don't get
  silently coerced to numbers).
