  in the exact OUTPUT_COLUMNS order, quoting every field (csv.QUOTE_ALL) to
  match the quoting style of the provided sample files.
  - I also edited pipeline.py to swap asyncio.gather for tqdm_asyncio.gather
  inside run_pipeline, so progress bars show up automatically for both the real
  run and the evaluation run, without duplicating the semaphore/task-list logic
  in main.py.

